  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1643621087" />
    <a title="Naturalbri (Bri Wignall)" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/34041104-naturalbri-bri-wignall"><img alt="Naturalbri (Bri Wignall)" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1421149815p2/34041104.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1643621087?book_show_action=true">May 20, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Naturalbri (Bri Wignall)" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Naturalbri (Bri Wignall)" href="/user/show/34041104-naturalbri-bri-wignall">Naturalbri (Bri Wignall)</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1643621087" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17990049289428253792">I am always a sucker for a good steampunk read. However, this book is so much more than &apos;just&apos; that. Not only is it a brilliantly written steampunk, but it is also a truly unique story, with depth and detail that create a world and time for you that are easy to become part of. Ultimately, I fell for this story, and very quickly. <br/><br/>The author&apos;s writing style had a way of creating excitement and action, whilst still lending time and pace to the slower, and much needed moments, of character developme</span>
  <span id="freeText17990049289428253792" style="display:none">I am always a sucker for a good steampunk read. However, this book is so much more than 'just' that. Not only is it a brilliantly written steampunk, but it is also a truly unique story, with depth and detail that create a world and time for you that are easy to become part of. Ultimately, I fell for this story, and very quickly. <br /><br />The author's writing style had a way of creating excitement and action, whilst still lending time and pace to the slower, and much needed moments, of character development and creation. There was a lot of thought and effort put in to each character. They all were very real and relatable, plus they built relationships and stories that were fun to become part of. <br /><br />I loved the whole idea of the story. It had a great steampunk feel to it, but with a quirky twist. I liked that you had a possible method to overcome this hold on life and death, but it was hidden, and our mains had both a need and a desire to discover the hidden truth. They had no idea what they would set in motion and what would come of it. <br /><br />Overall, this was a truly brilliant read. It was written well, had all the true aspects of a great steampunk read and really gave you everything you needed to become invested in and fall in love with the story. I highly recommend this book. <br /><br />**I received this book for free in exchange for my honest and unbiased opinion. <br /><br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="17990049289428253792" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
